                     <interp inst="t18261207-129-person790" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a blindmaker. I was in the road - I secured the prisoner, and took him to the officer's house; he then said, "My good woman, what is the amount of your loss - I will go to your husband and settle it."</p>
